## 8. Appendix

### Glossary

|  |  |
| --- | --- |
| Term | Definition |
| Full-body Embedding | Vector representation of entire function implementation |
| Persistent Graph | Code graph stored on disk, surviving server restarts |
| Incremental Update | Processing only changed files instead of full re-index |
| Content Hash | FNV-1a hash of file content for change detection |
| WAL | Write-Ahead Logging — SQLite journaling mode for crash safety |
| Chunking | Splitting large text into overlapping segments for embedding |

